import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; export default function Test10(){ const [productliste , setproductliste]=useState([]) const product=()=>{ fetch("https://fakestoreapi.com/products") .then((response) => response.json()) .then((response)=>setproductliste(response) ) } useEffect(()=>{ product() },[]) return(
ID Title Price Description Category Image Rating
) }
